{"nodes": [{"id": "home_michel_documentos_projects_hive_mind_cerebro_cloud_security_md", "label": "Cloud-Security.md", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "Cloud-Security.md", "source_location": "L1", "content": "# \ud83d\udd10 Seguran\u00e7a do Hive-Mind Cloud\n\nSeu c\u00e9rebro de IA agora pode ser acessado remotamente de forma segura.\n\n## \ud83d\ude80 Como expor para a Nuvem\nEu sugiro usar o **Tailscale Funnel** ou **Cloudflare Tunnels** para expor a porta `37702`.\n\n### Passo a Passo (Tailscale - Sugerido):\n1. Instale o Tailscale no seu PC e na VPS.\n2. No seu PC, rode: `tailscale serve 37702`.\n3. Sua API estar\u00e1 dispon\u00edvel em: `http://seu-pc.tailscale-ip:37702/api/v1/health`.\n\n## \ud83d\udd11 Autentica\u00e7\u00e3o\nTodos os endpoints (exceto health) exigem o header:\n`Authorization: Bearer <SUA_CHAVE_AQUI>`\n\nA chave \u00e9 configurada via vari\u00e1vel de ambiente:\n`HIVE_MIND_API_KEY`\n\n## \ud83d\udce1 Endpoints Dispon\u00edveis\n- `POST /api/v1/query`: Consulta h\u00edbrida (Texto + Vetores).\n- `POST /api/v1/observations`: Grava logs/decis\u00f5es remotas no seu banco local.\n- `GET /api/v1/semantic/related`: Recomenda\u00e7\u00e3o de notas (usado pelo Obsidian).\n\n---\n*Mantenha sua `HIVE_MIND_API_KEY` em segredo absoluto.*\n"}, {"id": "cerebro_cloud_security_seguran\u00e7a_do_hive_mind_cloud", "label": "\ud83d\udd10 Seguran\u00e7a do Hive-Mind Cloud", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "Cloud-Security.md", "source_location": "L1"}, {"id": "cerebro_cloud_security_como_expor_para_a_nuvem", "label": "\ud83d\ude80 Como expor para a Nuvem", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "Cloud-Security.md", "source_location": "L5"}, {"id": "cerebro_cloud_security_passo_a_passo_tailscale_sugerido", "label": "Passo a Passo (Tailscale - Sugerido):", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "Cloud-Security.md", "source_location": "L8"}, {"id": "cerebro_cloud_security_autentica\u00e7\u00e3o", "label": "\ud83d\udd11 Autentica\u00e7\u00e3o", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "Cloud-Security.md", "source_location": "L13"}, {"id": "cerebro_cloud_security_endpoints_dispon\u00edveis", "label": "\ud83d\udce1 Endpoints Dispon\u00edveis", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "Cloud-Security.md", "source_location": "L20"}], "edges": [{"source": "home_michel_documentos_projects_hive_mind_cerebro_cloud_security_md", "target": "cerebro_cloud_security_seguran\u00e7a_do_hive_mind_cloud", "relation": "contains", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "source_file": "Cloud-Security.md", "source_location": "L1", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "cerebro_cloud_security_seguran\u00e7a_do_hive_mind_cloud", "target": "cerebro_cloud_security_como_expor_para_a_nuvem", "relation": "contains", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "source_file": "Cloud-Security.md", "source_location": "L5", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "cerebro_cloud_security_como_expor_para_a_nuvem", "target": "cerebro_cloud_security_passo_a_passo_tailscale_sugerido", "relation": "contains", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "source_file": "Cloud-Security.md", "source_location": "L8", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "cerebro_cloud_security_seguran\u00e7a_do_hive_mind_cloud", "target": "cerebro_cloud_security_autentica\u00e7\u00e3o", "relation": "contains", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "source_file": "Cloud-Security.md", "source_location": "L13", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "cerebro_cloud_security_seguran\u00e7a_do_hive_mind_cloud", "target": "cerebro_cloud_security_endpoints_dispon\u00edveis", "relation": "contains", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "source_file": "Cloud-Security.md", "source_location": "L20", "weight": 1.0}], "input_tokens": 0, "output_tokens": 0}